    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban all sales of iceberg and glacial water in the UK.",
        "additional_details": "There are more and more companies using water collected from icebergs and glaciers to sell to the general public. This is absolutely reprehensible with the current issues facing the climate and it should be stopped as soon as possible. We cannot allow companies to bottle up and sell this precious resource as it's not sustainable.",
        "background": "Ban any products which contain ice water collected from icebergs or glaciers.",
